Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fn方正黑体_GBK}{\fad(300,1000)}「很多—」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断尾成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  敌人要逃跑了
