Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然共同作战很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的任务里用了很多回复药  能稍微分我点么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹰  用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹰想要的是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我不要
